data.meta_description: Our mission is to inspire, through science and education, a passion for nature, the protection of natural diversity, the fostering of health and leadership to a sustainable future.

Now Open!Through photos, specimens, casts, and lifelike reproductions, this exhibit tells the story of Lucy’s discovery, explores how she fits into the human family tree, and reveals how she informs our understanding of what makes us human. Learn More
